{"body": "For me it is more important to have the fallback on attribute names than on error messages - I just did the error messages part to complete the fallback cases.\r\nError messages are either the standard values for the type, could easily be set to non default I18n-Stings in validations (e.g. the :cannot_be_before_display_from error in the PublishRangeValidator in Humpyard) or are model specific in the most cases.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/439300", "created_at": "2010-09-30T13:32:33Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/39#issuecomment-439300", "updated_at": "2010-09-30T13:32:33Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 39, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/starpeak", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6ee7e5011c99cccffb54847b4013fc13?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F6b9938b3a148badea27e07af4ead5551.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/received_events", "gravatar_id": "6ee7e5011c99cccffb54847b4013fc13", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "starpeak", "type": "User", "id": 11974, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/starpeak/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52386dc3bd3543c151012d9b"}, "id": 439300, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/39"}
